org.apache.hive.service.auth.ldap

Interface SearchResultHandler.RecordProcessor

  • Enclosing class:
    SearchResultHandler

    public static interface SearchResultHandler.RecordProcessor
    An interface used by SearchResultHandler for processing records of a SearchResult on a per-record basis.
    Implementations of this interface perform the actual work of processing each record, but don't need to worry about exception handling, closing underlying data structures, and combining results from several search requests. SearchResultHandler

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods

      boolean process(SearchResult record)
